1:50.000Z","msg":"6成=普通 =唔升唔降<br />\n即係話 如果你有5唔會變4仲會令你份野用六成分升番做5 咁上下<br />\n<br />\n冇影響喇做咩唔溫 你話你得四成就降一級啫"},{"pid":"0ba206419ad80fee0b9081439321a0d007e05b9d","tid":585843,"uid":151134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9fc7f21c8797672aab8f8a2beeaed038bfbc604","tid":585843,"uid":34818,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"183061d057d66452b961f967a8c39c3c6fa8141d","tid":585843,"uid":151134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T04:29:23.000Z","msg":"利申2017 DSE 通識地理 5**<br />\n希望可以喺最後時間內幫助大家解決問題"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T04:31:57.000Z","msg":"通識ies得六成係咪唔好浪費時間係呢科<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T06:40:01.000Z","msg":"我IES都只係6 7 7 8夾埋都係7成幾 嗰陣見到個個都8 8 8 8以上即刻頹咗 但其實影響不大 我通識都係正正常常嘅分數（marginal）最後都冇問題 所以IES並唔好諗有幾嚴重 喺考評局對於通識一路收緊評分標準嘅前提下 6成幾追星係絕對有機會"},{"pid":"6457a9fc07524d7941f1ac66c05d404d40518542","tid":585843,"uid":151134,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76816d5406f62edc2b3663ddc79c4922bbefec69","tid":585843,"uid":111014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T05:22:28.000Z","msg":"你study leave個陣geog點溫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T06:43:06.000Z","msg":"我chem同geog上年隔咗10日考所以我有10日時間淨chur geog <br />\n同埋真係冇「點溫書」嘅問法 每個人對於溫書覺得迷惘嗰陣都有唔同嘅癥結喺度 你係框架唔熟？唔識寫essay？唔夠諗得快？map reading技巧？定某幾個topics冇信心<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bd9fc658353e64529fe0af23722c68de8443685","tid":585843,"uid":151134,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24bb0b02ad00a4f5d45c9f7fd112cdcd9eecea40","tid":585843,"uid":2002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T05:23:21.000Z","msg":"通識aim星 點溫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T06:49:22.000Z","msg":"留意考評局近年嘅趨勢係縮緊咗答題寬度 著重答題深度 上年我入考場考通識嘅時候見到4分1 pt 7分2 pts嘅時候我都頓咗頓 結果真係要每個pt都有晒框架 同埋時刻有個「how」喺個腦度<br />\n<br />\n不厭其煩地講多一次答題<br />\n1. 中心句（點出段落重心，i.e. 你成段都係想講呢件事）<br />\n2. 引用資料<br />\n3. 推論（記得不斷問how）<br />\n4. <strong>例子引援</strong>（我覺得係近年考評重心嚟！）<br />\n5. 總結（回應中心句成立）<br />\nExtra：多用<span style=\"color: red;\">由此可見，因此，儘管如此，所以，此外</span>等字眼，因為我去過考評局開放日體驗咗改卷，有呢啲領導字眼會令marker好睇超級多"},{"pid":"2205525346f150e04c613e8f7b50caceba8d8230","tid":585843,"uid":17825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T06:54:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7951b2f582d3323827521c2376c79211c9e4b7cb","tid":585843,"uid":34818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ba206419ad80fee0b9081439321a0d007e05b9d","tid":585843,"uid":151134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9fc7f21c8797672aab8f8a2beeaed038bfbc604","tid":585843,"uid":34818,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"183061d057d66452b961f967a8c39c3c6fa8141d","tid":585843,"uid":151134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T04:29:23.000Z","msg":"利申2017 DSE 通識地理 5**<br />\n希望可以喺最後時間內幫助大家解決問題"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T04:31:57.000Z","msg":"通識ies得六成係咪唔好浪費時間係呢科<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T06:40:01.000Z","msg":"我IES都只係6 7 7 8夾埋都係7成幾 嗰陣見到個個都8 8 8 8以上即刻頹咗 但其實影響不大 我通識都係正正常常嘅分數（marginal）最後都冇問題 所以IES並唔好諗有幾嚴重 喺考評局對於通識一路收緊評分標準嘅前提下 6成幾追星係絕對有機會"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T10:44:15.000Z","msg":"收到嗰分比連登D post 嚇到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  btw睇坊間通識書有用?定係有其他温書方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef1760ee24eac9685829e27e99ca94ba0599ddf2","tid":585843,"uid":151134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2205525346f150e04c613e8f7b50caceba8d8230","tid":585843,"uid":17825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T06:54:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":