34,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"06c4f9ce4b1629d34a17cd5a09e21e9f9fa95681","tid":585843,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T18:09:47.000Z","msg":"Ls答題有咩框架"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T05:59:03.000Z","msg":"睇返 #8"},{"pid":"7706ddbeda9cce0743a263057f8eb781c55d181d","tid":585843,"uid":147957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T06:12:37.000Z","msg":"想問例子引援 是資料外的例子？"},{"pid":"2471bd77dd35f54d795a5d6972a47db19c6e3bfb","tid":585843,"uid":151134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7706ddbeda9cce0743a263057f8eb781c55d181d","tid":585843,"uid":147957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T06:12:37.000Z","msg":"想問例子引援 是資料外的例子？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T06:48:16.000Z","msg":"係啊 <br />\n因為其實資料入面嘅嘢係人都會識抄寫 好多時都係加自己知道嘅例子會好好多<br />\n例如咁樣：（紅色嘅係例子）<br />\n題目：政治全球化對極端氣候的影響？<br />\n答案：政治全球化促使國際社會透過不同的會議及論壇，從而簽訂有效的應對協議，有助舒緩極端氣候問題。<span style=\"color: red;\">比如在2015年全球196國簽訂了巴黎協議，承諾共同對抗因工業及經濟活動而造成的溫室氣體排放問題</span>，從而透過國際社會的監察，能更有效地應對極端氣候。<br />\n以上就係其他考生未必能夠講到嘅嘢，如果你講到係會impress個marker<br />\n另外就係千萬唔好嘗試自己去捏造數據同例子出嚟，因為個marker知道嘅嘢一定多過你，真係俾佢識穿咗係會偷雞唔成蝕把米"},{"pid":"1a2a04b6b5fca8d6c3107d01e06a8d9a225af243","tid":585843,"uid":151134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f547356b779fa5246d4193dab9ade322e0e41fa4","tid":585843,"uid":34818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a37d2a014e6a490bcf4a5ca303b81b906f97a3a","tid":585843,"uid":151134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"029aa5f4fe07c933948603ffcf1bda6b1507860e","tid":585843,"uid":34818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T15:03:39.000Z","msg":"如果要溫書都係操pp?定係睇多啲書 我得呢兩本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/09/230308_4b6956f3c871e973f08b361fce3b1ded.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F09