pan style=\"font-size: x-small;\">DSE得4既9up</span>"},{"pid":"ed43d9c5b74a1d68e0bc5ecd9b68e01dee0b47e9","tid":585843,"uid":69734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T15:46:49.000Z","msg":"我想問下Geog internal process DBQ可以點考？"},{"pid":"badb6f441c26deac697ab5c503e24df37fa8d223","tid":585843,"uid":69734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed43d9c5b74a1d68e0bc5ecd9b68e01dee0b47e9","tid":585843,"uid":69734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T15:46:49.000Z","msg":"我想問下Geog internal process DBQ可以點考？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T15:47:11.000Z","msg":"今年應該會出internal？"},{"pid":"72904cc9cc660bed901d5051efc347b6cc917064","tid":585843,"uid":24235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T16:03:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ff980606e97f0b4c49504d5982c1d0740876a83","tid":585843,"uid":10966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T16:32:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好迷惘 硬係唔太知點樣推論得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>因果關係搞清楚 學術啲講就係我地要令成個推論冇hidden assumption<br />\n考下你 智能電話普及導致家庭關係惡化 你會點推論？</blockquote><br />\n智能電話普及，大部分港人也有至少一部手智能電話，形成長期機不離手的習慣，成為低頭族。<br />\n基於智能電話內有不同的手機程式和遊戲程式，使智能電話的吸引度大增。當成年人長期專注在手機時，例如在吃飯時只顧手上的智能手機，親子溝通的時間便會減少，兩者彷佛形成一層隔閡，使親子關係疏離。長期以説，兩者在長期缺乏有效溝通下，易生磨擦，甚至衝突，使家庭關係惡化。<br />\n<br />\n唔太識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf694b3b78baa813fbd306f579748ec58fba8e6c","tid":585843,"uid":30817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T17:57:46.000Z","msg":"Geog lv4上5會唔會好困難？"},{"pid":"18d148cef92ad2a5444ccf3ffe43390db95fca9f","tid":585843,"uid":151134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"badb6f441c26deac697ab5c503e24df37fa8d223","tid":585843,"uid":69734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"